data.description: It's time to make this adorable home YOURS! This darling 4 bed 2 bath home is inviting, well maintained, and has many updates. As you make your way out back, you'll find an oversized fenced yard and an open patio perfect to enjoy those summer days. The home has ample parking both on the long driveway and street parking. It is near parks, schools, and town.
